        <description>&lt;h2 id=&#34;welcome&#34;&gt;Welcome!
&lt;/h2&gt;&lt;p&gt;On this site you will find &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://jankazimir.github.io/pages/archives/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;posts&lt;/a&gt; about projects I&amp;rsquo;ve build, my journey building them and topics related to programming and .&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Expect no expertise, only a stubborn penchant for learning and a thirst for improvement.
Enjoy.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;h3 id=&#34;about-me&#34;&gt;About Me
&lt;/h3&gt;&lt;p&gt;I began programming in 2025 with web development before moving towards Data Analysis and Machine Learning. You can find some of my projects on &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://github.com/JanKazimir&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;GitHub&lt;/a&gt;.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;I am currently enrolled at &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;https://becode.org/&#34;  target=&#34;_blank&#34; rel=&#34;noopener&#34;
    &gt;Becode&lt;/a&gt;, in the AI/Data Science course and looking for an internship (here is my &lt;a class=&#34;link&#34; href=&#34;CV_EN%20Jan%20Kazimirowski%2024may%20copy.pdf&#34; &gt;resume&lt;/a&gt;).&lt;/p&gt;
